column5: And some of you guys thought you were good??? Check this guy out.   The Ultimate Steelheader
Just awesome, Dan! And that doubleheader is WOW!
That was COOL. Now the question is... is he fishing a river or a great lake where 2 talons at a time are legal ?

That was so cool !!!! .  .... he sure looks like he knows what hes doing,man those talons are sharp !!!!    those trout dont stand a chance.  ..imagine rainbow trout dinners 7 days a week.  .LOL..LOL..LOL thanks for sharing dan,i saved it and want to show a few birds of prey lovers.....cheers
WOW!!! Remind me to never cross his line when drifting....LOL.  Those are some amazing pics!
thanks Dan those pics are incerdible!
I can't imagine taking those pictures,  just wonderful.  thx, danc.
When I read the Title I thought we would see Pictures of NATE , Awesome  pics, makes it look so effortless swoop down grab and away ...
Thanks for sharing.   Those were incredible pictures.
Awesome pics! Based on my count however, I believe that bird is over it's daily limit! Thanks Dan! HH
thanks for posting that, it was reall cool!
